creator: ChampaLars Holdings Private Limited
descriptionHtml:
Explore Kudadoo Maldives Private Island and its stunning facilities and discover more about the moments of magnificence that await as part of the "Anything. Anytime. Anywhere." fully-inclusive concept.

Use this App as an addition to your personal Butler service at Kudadoo. Complete the check in formalities before you arrive, directly in the App. During your stay the App provides the perfect travel companion, showing your Thajuribaa of your culinary journey, experiences and effortless adventures.

About Kudadoo Maldives Private Island:
Kudadoo Maldives Private Island offers a fully-inclusive experience that makes everything under the moon available to you at any time and anywhere. Bound to impress even the most discerning traveller, this private island has been designed for escapes from the confines of everyday life.

Moments of magnificence take the form of delightful culinary creations, unlimited leisure activities and wellness. Seize your days on this petite tropical island with the assistance of your personal & virtual butler who can help you curate the perfect holiday itinerary.

Kudadoo sets a new standard in sustainable luxury hospitality and is the Maldives' only fully solar-powered private island.

Use the App to help:
- check in to the resort prior to arrival
- discover the moments of magnificence that await you at the resort
- view your Thajuribaa of hand picked experiences from your personal Butler
- book your next stay at the resort
